@startuml SD-08_AdminManagement
!theme cerulean-outline
title SD-08: Admin — Quan Ly Tai Khoan Nguoi Dung

actor Admin
participant "Frontend\n(React + Vite)" as FE
participant "UserController\n(Spring Boot)" as UCtrl
participant "UserService" as USvc
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

== Xem danh sach tai khoan ==
Admin -> FE : Vao trang quan ly user
FE -> UCtrl : GET /api/users\nAuthorization: Bearer <JWT>
note over UCtrl : @PreAuthorize("hasRole('ADMIN')")
UCtrl -> USvc : getAllUsers()
USvc -> DB : SELECT * FROM users\nORDER BY user_id
DB --> USvc : List<User>
USvc --> UCtrl : List<UserResponse>
UCtrl --> FE : 200 OK\n[{userId, name, email, role, status}]
FE --> Admin : Hien thi bang user voi actions

== Thay doi vai tro ==
Admin -> FE : Click "Thay doi Role"\nchon role moi (TEACHER/STUDENT/ADMIN)
FE -> UCtrl : PUT /api/users/{userId}/role\n{role: "TEACHER"}\nAuthorization: Bearer <JWT>
UCtrl -> USvc : updateUserRole(userId, newRole)
USvc -> DB : UPDATE users SET role = ?\nWHERE user_id = ?
DB --> USvc : Updated User
USvc --> UCtrl : UserResponse {role: "TEACHER"}
UCtrl --> FE : 200 OK\n{userId, role: "TEACHER", ...}
FE --> Admin : Cap nhat UI — role da thay doi

== Soft-delete tai khoan (BR-04) ==
Admin -> FE : Click "Vo hieu hoa tai khoan"
FE -> UCtrl : PUT /api/users/{userId}/status\n{status: "INACTIVE"}\nAuthorization: Bearer <JWT>
UCtrl -> USvc : updateUserStatus(userId, INACTIVE)
USvc -> DB : UPDATE users SET status = 'INACTIVE'\nWHERE user_id = ?
note over DB : BR-04: Chi soft-delete\nkhong xoa du lieu that
DB --> USvc : OK
USvc --> UCtrl : UserResponse {status: "INACTIVE"}
UCtrl --> FE : 200 OK
FE --> Admin : Tai khoan da bi vo hieu hoa
@enduml

